    "body": "Hmm, we definitely want to serialize the integer that the size is larger than 256 bits (currently, `uint384` in the spec). I think maybe we can add a new rule for tree hash, e.g.,\r\n* `uint0, ..., uint256`: return the serialization of the value.\r\n* `uint264, ... uintN`: return the hash of the serialization of the value.",
